		<h1 class="text-[#804422] text-4xl text-center mt-12 font-semibold mb-2 julius-sans-one-regular">Quien Quiero Ser?</h1>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-9 grid-rows-7 gap-4 text-center min-h-[600px] min-w-[1200px] ">
